      Who got Golden Boot in ISL 2020?
      Igor Angulo
      2020-21 ISL Golden Boot winner Igor Angulo

      Igor Angulo winning the ISL 2020-21 Golden Boot, edging out ATK Mohun Bagan talisman Roy Krishna on technicality. Both players ended with 14 goals each, but Angulo won the coveted prize since he had taken lesser minutes (1,645) than Krishna (2,062) to get his tally.      13-Mar-2021
